main event: A UFO sighting report from McGuire AFB, New Jersey on January 17, 1965, describing an object observed for approximately 1 minute.
interesting points: The object was described as probably being an aircraft,The observation was visual and involved a single object,The sighting was classified as unclassified with no photographs available,The object appeared to be flying in a level flight at 12,000 feet,No physical evidence was found accompanying the sighting.
sighted object: unknown aerial object presumed to be an aircraft
